                        <p class="app_title">Find Real Food: The WAPF Shopping Guide for the Highest Quality Foods Available</p>
                        <p>Healthy grocery shopping can be such a challenge with so many brands to choose from and tricky labels that hide harmful ingredients! It’s hard to know what to buy, no matter if you are into Traditional diets, Paleo, Primal, Vegetarian, or GAPS diet. Good quality “Real Food” is at the foundation of every one of them!</p>
                        <p>In this easy-to-use grocery guide, several thousands of food and beverage products from 30 different categories have been meticulously researched by the Weston A. Price Foundation (WAPF), a not-for-profit organization founded in 1999, dedicated to education, research, and activism on health promoting, traditionally prepared, nutrient-dense, whole foods in the human diet.</p>
                        <p>Save time and money and improve your health by using this guide, created by nutrition experts who researched which products and brands are best. Each category of food must uphold specific quality standards in order to qualify for the guide.</p>
                        <p>For example, “Best” rated foods are in their whole form, have no additives, artificial flavors, MSG, or trans-fats. Dairy and beef must come from grassfed or pasture-raised (free-range) cows. Eggs must come from pastured hens that are preferably not fed soy. Veggies and fruit must be organic or biodynamic, preferably local and in season.</p>
                        <p>Once a user of this app, you become part of the “Find Real Food” community, and can rank or review products listed so you can learn from others’ experiences, and share your own. You can also suggest new foods or brands to be reviewed by the Foundation.</p>
